content:
Preparing to Use Agent Home

To let your agents see their shift schedules, set up Agent Home in Workforce Engagement.

Workforce Engagement is available in Lightning Experience and requires Enterprise, Performance, or Unlimited Editions.

Assign the Workforce Engagement Agent permission set to your agents.
Create a service resource for each agent who uses Agent Home.
Check that the Agent Home tab is on (if org was created before Summer '21).
Create an Apex trigger to let agents see their assigned shifts.
title: Setting Up Agent Home in Service Cloud
